text: François Louis Joseph de Wargny (19 September 1750 – 3 November 1816) was a French-born Dutch politician. Wargny was an administrator and landowner from Mechelen. For the Antwerp provincie he served as a member of the House of Representatives from 1815. During his period Wargny died on 3 November 1816 at the age of 66. ==References== Category:1750 births Category:1816 deaths Category:Dutch politicians Category:Members of the House of Representatives of the Netherlands
title: François Louis Joseph de Wargny
